---
title: Sugar Snap Stir-fried Pork with fluffy rice and fried peppers
description: This teriyaki pork mince stir-fry is the ultimate quick and easy meal. It's so effortless to prepare, in fact, that you might be surprised by how delicious a dish it is. With tender fried peppers and sugar snap peas for added colour and crunch, this is a simple dish that's not to be missed.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R03_W15_IE_IEXFQP0064-4_Main_high-57895e29.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/sugar-snap-stir-fried-pork-63d8f2e6dd4a18d65316b035-b7f144a3.pdf
